Dirvish is a fast, disk based, rotating network backup system.

With dirvish you can maintain a set of complete images of your
filesystems with unattended creation and expiration. A dirvish
backup vault is like a time machine for your data.

Dirvish was originally created by jw schultz .

after installation, see DIRVISH.CONF(5)

requires:
 perl-time-parsedate
 perl-time-period

